    MODERN SLIP-ON SNEAKERS WITH RUNNING-INSPIRED STYLE.
    A celebrated racer style is transformed with a sleek slip-on design. These shoes have a woven upper that's locked in with a wide strap. A contrast adidas logo stands out across the front. Plush midsole cushioning propels every step with comfort.
